PrecisReappointment of PAUL CANTOR of Toronto, Ontario, as a director of the Public Sector Pension Investment Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term of one year; and designation of PAUL CANTOR as Chairperson of the Public Sector Pension Investment Board: effective March 5, 2011.
